{
  "stem": "27767.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Naturally better than we had before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some of them, they were trying at the time to organize to go to Palestine or to go to America.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And but we didn't know at that time what's-- and when I find out my brother is alive--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I find out, somebody came from Romania back at that time to Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was trying to get to America.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was telling me, look, your brother is alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He is in Romania.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He escaped the labor camp, and the Russians liberated him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I decided-- because until then, I was thinking not to go back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But deep in my heart, I was always thinking maybe I will find somebody from my sister, from my mother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even they told me it was crematoriums and this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But deep in my heart, I said maybe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe they did escape some way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe I find somebody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I decided to go back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Besides, I find out about my father-- my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Maybe if my brother would not be there, I would never have gone back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But thank God he was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Romania, at that time we went with some-- they took us with some trains and very bad transportation, about three weeks until we got to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother was-- he heard about the people are coming back from the camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he found out about myself, I'm coming back with a train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was waiting every day, after the trains there, when they come in, if somebody comes from the family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was there at the train station, rail station, when I came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then we went-- actually, we find out later.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
